{
  "stem": "26576.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So my mother put on a scarf, so she looked like a peasant woman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we traveled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And it took us a while to come to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We were very scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We came to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Warsaw was a horror at that stage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a place-- some very distant relatives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Warsaw was completely-- Warsaw was so-- I mean, everybody knows it now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was, almost everything was in ruins.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very, very-- Sosnowiec was not, because they came in without completely-- nobody sort had enough time to say a thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in Warsaw, there were fights.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got that family of ours, and we stayed with them a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we organized a horse and carriage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it took us a night again, and we came to [POLISH] Losice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the second time in my life that I came there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- I hadn't-- I didn't even remember it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a village.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But later on, I read it was a village 99% Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not a little-- it was a shtetl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was quite-- so like a village where there was a lot of Jews at that stage.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But this was a point-- [POLISH] Losice was a point.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was not far.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What I didn't explain that there was a Molotov-Ribbentrop Pact.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in this pact they divided Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The River Bug divided Poland in two parts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The East belonged-- so the Russian took.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the West, the Germans took.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were in the German occupied zone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So what we tried very hard-- it took us quite a few months of planning at that-- how do we get to that Russian occupied zone, which was a very hard thing.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
